neatDraw.dataPanels

Class SpeciesPopulationSizes

  • java.lang.Object
    • neatDraw.DataPanel
      • neatDraw.dataPanels.SpeciesPopulationSizes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<DataPanel>

    public class SpeciesPopulationSizes
extends DataPanel
    This DataPanel displays the population of each species over time by representing a species' population with a polygon color coded to that species' color. The height of each polygon represents that species' population. (Time measured in generations is on the X axis.)
